text: Princess of the Nile is a 1954 American adventure movie. It was directed by Harmon Jones. Actors include Debra Paget, Jeffrey Hunter, Michael Rennie, Dona Drake, Michael Ansara, Edgar Barrier, and Wally Cassell. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:1954 adventure movies Category:American adventure movies Category:Movies directed by Harmon Jones
